The paper discusses privacy-preserving solutions for the Internet of Things, which is a topic related to computer security (cs.CR), information retrieval (cs.IR), cybernetics (cs.CY), social and information networks (cs.SI), and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). However, since the focus is on privacy, cs.CR is the most likely category.
